name: playerCount
description: The Number of players participating in the given game.

name: selectionDuration
description: how many seconds do participants have to complete a tangram selection trial

name: feedbackDuration
description: how many seconds the feedback is displayed for

name: listenerBonus
description: how much a listener is paid per correct answer (in cents)

name: speakerBonus
description: how much bonus the speaker gets *per listener* who gets it right

name: targetSet
description: which set of imagesets to use

name: numTargets
description: how many images are shown at once

name: repsPerBlock
description: how many trials are there per image set

name: scale
description: what the utilities are multiplied by -- should be low for coop and high for competitive

name: chatEnabled
description: to enable or disable the language conditions
